Question: The left image shows exactly three women, the right image shows four or more woman, and all women are wearing two piece swimsuits that are not the same color as each other.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/736x/49/2e/a2/492ea2faf8297156572c376acf2653c5--dakota-fanning-hot-body.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/originals/4b/82/12/4b82123405d6b04ed9af2930b4485ae8.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many women are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many women are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are all women wearing two piece swimsuits?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are all women wearing two piece swimsuits?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the swimsuits not the same color as each other?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the swimsuits not the same color as each other?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 3 and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} >= 4 and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} and {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
